{"tid":348821,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教] 拍足球片買咩Cam好？","createTime":"2017-08-06T05:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T00:37:40.000Z","uid":52123,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7cabe48d3437d8ef805319f2f12a2ff7a8b839b","tid":348821,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"話說小弟同班朋友仔踢波，呢半年開始，借左用人地部入門級單反拍片，當紀錄下賽後檢討咁。不過開始發覺太重、角度又窄，而且最主要係借機果位朋友唔肯再借（因為都幾密）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同班波友傾過，可以夾錢買部機，最緊要輕便，但筆直有限只有$800-$1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚踢波為主（雖然有大燈但都有d暗）、踢開大硬地場例如維園咁、已有腳架<br />\n<br />\n真係乜都唔熟，係咪應該買sony DV？<br />\naction cam例如sjcam sj6、soocoo s1果d又掂唔掂？<br />\n跪求推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一定要：夠輕身夠細；機背螢幕preview；角度夠wide<br />\n最好有：拍到1.5hours+；4k；zoom in-out"},{"pid":"25b2c3918a971c04471b678fdb99a82446b772b3","tid":348821,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"打漏左個0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470814835d25825adc18d0734469712a16f935c0","tid":348821,"uid":523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:19:34.000Z","msg":"咪撚夾錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班人先夾得800-1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己返一個月兼職買部a6300 自己用咪算"},{"pid":"16552a77e5ba4f6f2e74cfd735a6079612283a55","tid":348821,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"夾錢果度係on9，我明，但無計啦，唔係我唔肯夾，嘈都嘈過&hellip;&hellip;你懂的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以呢家唯有將價就貨，始終部嘢買返嚟都係Share用，唔係私伙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打屌得細力d <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef297697610b477da2ad95c677c7fd4198018aac","tid":348821,"uid":27165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"山狗 幾百有"},{"pid":"97519b9b6a359be2e18702389fce25992b76dee6","tid":348821,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山狗 幾百有</blockquote><br />\n呢家睇緊sjcam sj6同soocoo牌子，但始終未用過action cam，拍踢波（咁大個球場，十鳩幾個人）又夜晚o唔ok？"},{"pid":"1afae4fcef9fec761aac947860a0346bf6494bac","tid":348821,"uid":27165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山狗 幾百有</blockquote><br />\n呢家睇緊sjcam sj6同soocoo牌子，但始終未用過action cam，拍踢波（咁大個球場，十鳩幾個人）又夜晚o唔ok？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以上youtube搵下片 睇sample"},{"pid":"6d1eed5ad3ee2d6bc5f76a1b8155cf270f10b360","tid":348821,"uid":123196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"講真，是但攞部手機加wide lens都已經好過曬上述例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你用iPhone 咪買粒moment wide lens"},{"pid":"ff5728d1d10205f644eaa2e26154a1b3f6bd52ac","tid":348821,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"買部二手機啦"},{"pid":"cfdded1440bfbe1f5a10a9786a445380dba43927","tid":348821,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"800-1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家輪流用手機影啦"},{"pid":"3f015bc831f803afa171b5b6d1c9b56b00c90e13","tid":348821,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"211690bb8a58ce6c4769fffa101d852663e821e1","tid":348821,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"以為拍咩比賽片 <img src=