te><blockquote><blockquote>賽後檢討定打飛機先<br />\n1000一齊食餐飯算數啦</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 樓主講到佢地咁唔團結 連夾錢買機都無人想夾 拎去食餐飯 和和氣氣 之後咪大家都肯夾錢囉</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係唔團結既，但無啦啦又比多舊錢，收錢果個都好麻煩，有組過隊就明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學生?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">組一隊波玩，又波衫又裝備又買場又球證，其實果度唔少錢，最煩係&hellip;收錢</span></blockquote><br />\n咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如你放條片上黎，自己嘅又好人地嘅又好<br />\n起碼知道你想拍乜先</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YxhTzHJScN4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYxhTzHJScN4&d=RXwih5i%2FRi3UFcgrGh8mwcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=87997aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YxhTzHJScN4</a><br />\n利：無踢呢個聯賽，唔是我</blockquote><br />\n你地平時有一個人負責拍？</blockquote><br />\n想用咁樣效果一定要DV 啦<br />\n最平 SONY CX405 水貨大約1.5K<br />\n無得再平"},{"pid":"e9e3f885291c11063fa87c70f0061268121d2b4e","tid":348821,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩咁多位巴打屌得細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我自己都有用開中階機拍片，當然唔係話好高汁果d，純粹紀錄下，但部機就黎比人地，所以先開post問<br />\n<br />\naround$1000其實好多非go-pro、sony既action cam都做到4k/30fps、1080p/60fps，買多粒後備電肯定夠拍2hrs，但我未試過用action cam wide住長開咁夜拍運動片所以先問下意見，同埋邊間廠相對較好咁解<br />\n<br />\n夾錢呢家野人人問題唔同，又唔係我唔肯出，無計啵大佬&hellip;&hellip;現階段爭取緊去到~$4000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab4de5ac4152344e8bdb0d04893fc245de6ef46","tid":348821,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夾錢買部機，最緊要輕便，但筆直有限只有$800-$1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ??</blockquote><br />\n又話有腳架，又嫌部入門單反重，仲話踢波<br />\n我睇唔透"},{"pid":"04fb8027a446358a3d3eb09